      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just a \"crisis\" tho. it's reality. i'm 35. i have nothing left to build with. everyone is going to look at me and just see a failure. it's like the version of me that mattered just died today anyway. there's no \"path forward\" when the foundation is just gone. it feels more like an ending than a setback.",
